reviews_data.review_text: I have been waiting for Giddy Goat to open in this southend location for SO long, and by the looks of today’s soft opening, I wasn’t the only one!! The space was big, clean, and beautiful. The empanadas were all delicious. I can’t wait to come back with my family, friends, and my dog!! Everyone there was so nice and the atmosphere was positive and so welcoming. It exceeded my expectations. Welcome to the neighborhood, Giddy Goat! We didn’t go to the upstairs patio, but I saw lots of people heading up there.

Finally open! Excited to report that the new south end location has the same delicious empanadas and excellent coffee as their Plaza Midwood flagship store. Awesome remote work setup with a spacious and modern warehouse feel. Great service as expected. Can’t wait to sit on the patio in the warmer weather!
